When you configure the Inventory module in Acumatica ERP, you should configure basic processes, such as the full physical inventory. Organizations perform physical inventory to obtain accurate numbers of goods in stock.{br}
In this section, you will read about the basic configuration of physical inventory and the types of physical inventory available in Acumatica ERP. ==In This Chapter==[anchor|#_9fb12d92-2d10-486f-9d7f-e9dd6f7f96dd] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#_c33afd47-4a86-45cf-bbab-d3eb34d896f6] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__con_Planning_for_Physical_Inventory|Configuration of Physical Inventory] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__con_Physical_Inventory_Types|Types of Physical Inventory]
| [anchor|#_40aea7af-1162-45f4-9418-0ad34dafcb83] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__How_Create_Full_Count_PI_Type|To Create a PI Type for a Full Count]
