In Acumatica ERP, you can configure automated replenishment for stock items at your organization&rsquo;s warehouses.((({S:Hint}The functionality that supports automated replenishment is available if the ''Inventory Replenishment'' feature is enabled on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\CS_10_00_00|Enable/Disable Features] ([~/?ScreenId=CS100000|CS100000]) form. ))) If the ''Multiple Warehouses'' feature is enabled on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\CS_10_00_00|Enable/Disable Features] form, you can assign different replenishment methods to different items of inventory stocked at different warehouses and enter warehouse-specific item settings (such as safety stock, reorder point, and maximum quantity) to be used as parameters for these methods. Different items may require diverse parameters because of varying customer demand for the items and different numbers of days required to receive the requested quantities from the vendors. If the ''Multiple Warehouses'' feature is disabled on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\CS_10_00_00|Enable/Disable Features] form, you can assign replenishment classes to particular stock items.{br}
By using forecast models, you can fine-tune such parameters as safety stock, reorder point, and maximum quantities based on sales statistics. Thus, by using automated replenishment, your company can strike a balance between overstocks and stockouts.{br}
In this chapter, you will read about automated replenishment and availability calculation in Acumatica ERP. ==In This Chapter==[anchor|#_27dfda01-84b5-432e-81ac-89d96d5f40e2] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#ul_arn_lnl_3n] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__con_Automated_Replenishment|Automated Replenishment] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__con_Configuration_of_Automated_Replenishment|Configuration of Automated Replenishment] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__con_Replenishment_Parameters|Replenishment Methods and Their Parameters] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__con_Replenishment_Based_on_Demand_Forecast_Model|Replenishment Parameters Based on Demand Forecast ] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__con_Example_Replenishment_Calculation|An Example of Replenishment Parameter Calculation] *[HelpRoot_InvMgmt\IN__con_Availability_Calculation|Availability Calculation]
